adjectives.description: unworkable (comparative more unworkable, superlative most unworkable)

entries.meaning: Not workable or operable; not practical; unmanageable.
Something that is not workable, or cannot be made to work.
examples: We all have some secret little hope that the unworkables will be resurrected. You haven't seen any of the occupants of the pyramids pull this off yet, nor will you see any use for old, outdated, dead office stuff.
